description: Tables showing a) Breast screening programme coverage of women (less than 3 years since last test) aged 53-64 for the years 2001/02 to 2005/06, broken down by Primary Care Organisation; 5 p. b) Cervical screening programme coverage of the Target Age Group (25-64) less than 5 yrs since last adequate test for the years 2001/02 to 2006/07, broken down by Primary Care Organisation. 8 p.
